title: Reports of a second explosion in Lahore
text:
Reports of a second explosion in Lahore | 0 0 
LAHORE: There are reports of a second explosion in the Gulberg area of the city. Earlier seven people were killed in a blast in the DHA area of the city in which 17 others were injured. According to initial reports, the explosion took place next to a fast food restaurant.
